title: Steele gets his season off to an ideal start at Silverado
text:
> Sports Steele gets his season off to an ideal start at Silverado Rory McIlroy, of Northern Ireland, hits from the fourth tee of the Silverado Resort North Course during the first round of the Frys.com PGA Tour golf tournament Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Napa, Calif.
